Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.67,0:22:42.47,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3}回首身后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.93,0:22:45.64,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}眼中有了你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.72,0:22:49.39,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,180)\blur3\3c&HE49B44&}我们四目相对
